current directory or in vmpath if specified.
.PP
.br
\f[B]Options:\f[R]
.PP
.br
Boolean values are either \f[C]true\f[R] or \f[C]false\f[R].
For example, to build
.PD 0
.P
.PD
.br
a minimal distribution, add to command line:
.PD 0
